<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body: {
            color: black;
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="width: 100%; background-image: url('cid:background'); background-repeat: no-repeat;">
      <img src="cid:logo" width="400px" style="display: flex; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-top: 100px;" />
      <div style="width: 45%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <p>Hey {{name}},</p>
        <p>Ho-Ho-Hold on to your Santa hats! Your Secret Santa event is just a week away, and the excitement is snowballing! 🎉❄️</p>
        <p>📅 Date: {{eventDate}}</p>
        <p>⏰ Time: {{eventTime}}</p>
        <p>📍 Location: [Event Location]</p>
        <p>Here are some jolly good reminders to keep you on the 'nice' list as we dash towards the big day:</p>
        <p>Gift Gathering: If your Secret Santa gift is still lounging in the sleigh, now's the time to wrap it up! Remember, it’s not just the thought that counts, but the wrapping too!</p>
        <p>Santa's Secret: Remember, the identity of your giftee is a secret as guarded as Santa's workshop. Keep the mystery alive!</p>
        <p>We can’t wait to see you all in your festive cheer, sharing gifts and making this holiday season one to remember.</p>
        <p>Looking forward to a fa-la-la-la-fantastic time!</p>
        <p>Warm wishes,</p>
        <p>{{ownerName}}</p>
        <p>P.S. Keep practicing your 'surprised' face for when you receive your gift – we're aiming for Oscar-level performances here! 🎭🎁</p>
      </div>
  </body>
</html>
